casebody.data:
William STEPHENS, Director, Texas Department of Criminal Justice, Correctional Institutions Division, petitioner,
v.
Nelson GONGORA. No. 13-592. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 13, 2014.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
